<h3 id="compile">Compile</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Change directory into the project name
    <div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code> <span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">cd </span>hello
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Edit file <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">src/main.rs</code> with the blinky code</li>
  <li>Edit <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Cargo.toml</code> to add dependancies</li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/esp-rs/esp-idf-template#build">Compile / build</a> the project
    <div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>  <span class="nv">$ </span>cargo build
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

<h2 id="upload-the-firmware">Upload the firmware</h2>

<ol>
  <li>Plug in the board into the USB port (not the UART port).</li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/esp-rs/esp-idf-template#flash">Upload / Flash</a>
    <div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>  espflash /dev/cu.usbmodem14101 target/xtensa-esp32s3-espidf/debug/hello
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

<h2 id="view-the-logs">View the logs</h2>

<p>Start the <a href="https://github.com/esp-rs/esp-idf-template#monitor">serial monitor</a></p>
<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>  espmonitor /dev/cu.usbmodem14101
</code></pre></div></div>
:ET